{
  "chapter": 40,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲与徐子陵随素素抵达荥阳大龙头府，翟娇将二人视作奴才，安排在食房做粗重工作。素素夜间来访，透露李密曾强占她的遭遇，二人义愤填膺欲带素素逃离，素素最终同意。次日二人试图出府购买逃生工具，被家将张厉阻拦。龙头府总管屠叔方识破二人身怀绝技，盘问后对二人深表赏识，承诺向翟娇争取改善待遇，并提出传授十二手擒拿截脉法。此时沈落雁在府外监视，翟让与李密正攻打兴洛仓，二人暂留龙头府修炼武功。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再说一吹来给我听听。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "不知当时小姐是到了哪裹呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在是我问你还是你问我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "请问小姐大龙头是否在府内！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "奴才好胆，你是聋的吗？尽说多馀话，是否要给我打一顿才肯守规矩。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你看来老实点，由你来说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "请小姐垂询。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们凭甚么爬上屋梁去，以爹的功夫，怎会不知你们躲在那裹。更何况以爹的功夫，就算有人躲在箱子内要偷袭他，亦不会得手；我看爹一点都没有受过伤的样子，那被袭的人定不是我爹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "这事很容易弄清楚只要小姐问问大龙头，不是可以分晓了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "闭嘴，谁准你说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "我要说的正是这几句，找大龙头一问便可真相大白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这事我自有分寸，你们就留在这里，待爹回来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "要等多久呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "十大八天吧，谁说得上来。你们懂做甚么，我可不能自养你们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "请问小姐，现在我可以说话吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "快说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "text": "我们可否休息几天，待大龙头回来后才决定做甚工作！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhai_jiao",
      "speaker_name": "翟娇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知你是爱偷懒的家伙。昨晚还休息得不够吗？刚巧食房缺人，你们就到那里帮手吧。记着，不准你们对任何人说出那件事，否则我就斩了你们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不明白小姐为何待你们特别差，但两位好弟弟忍着点吧。大龙头回来后，一切便会不同的了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我看她是恼我们揭破她曾被人掳走的事，她是那么要面子的人，当然不高兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不要那样说她好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "现在你小姐已清楚事情的始末，姐姐亦尽了责任，不若我们立刻离开，到洛阳去找李大哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素素姐难道不想李大哥吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想又有甚么用？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们的李人哥志比天高，对儿女之情那会放在心上，求你们以后都不要把他和人家拉在一起好吗？何况我根本配不起他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们还末有机会告诉姐姐别后的追遇，还不说来给姐姐听。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位弟弟真坏，整天想去逛妓院。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "都是寇仲的主意，我只是被迫而已。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你这家伙只懂赖在我身上，你自己没有这个心吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要说了，男人都是这样的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要不要姊姊伺候你们呢？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素素姐！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐既可陪别的男人，你们又不是我的亲弟弟，有关系呢？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姐姐怎可去和别的男人好？李大哥…嘿…",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姐姐只是奴婢的身分，主子有命便要依从，那能为自己作主。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去找那婆娘拚命！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "不关小姐事！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "那关谁的事呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时小姐尚未回来，老爷在府内款待手下，密公也来了，那晚我出来侍宴，有人向老爷要我，老爷就答应了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是他！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "你不说出来，我们就当是他好了。翟老头亦非好人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老爷也是无可奈何的，自荥阳大胜后，人人都说功劳尽属密公，蒲山公营的人更是气焰高张，唉，我是不该告诉你们的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "早叫素素姐不要回来了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你们该知姐姐为何不愿见到李大哥了。何况他只当我是个小妹子，事情发生后，姐姐再不想活，但总觉得你们吉人有天相，才忍辱偷生，希望有重见你们的一天，现在终达成心愿。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "素素姐万勿有轻生之念，我们今晚就走，只要找到钓索一类的东酉，我们便有把握将姐姐带走，以后我们姐弟再不会分开了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姐姐还留恋甚么呢？是否…嘿…",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要乱猜，我恨不得将那贼碎尸万段，只是念着小姐的恩情。唉，这样好吗？待老爷回来后，把事情说清楚，姐姐就全依你们意思好了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "翟让一听便知事情真伪，我们留下来亦没有甚么意思，姐姐若下了决心随我们离开，明天我们便溜出府外张罗逃生工具，入黑即走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最紧要是避过沈婆娘的耳目。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我一边洗碗，一边练功，都不知多么写意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这几天我明显感到体内的真气愈来愈听差使，你试试把真气运在耳鼓穴，连远处的人低声说我们闲话都可听得一清二楚呢。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "回去后定要试试，现在买东西要紧，这大龙头府死气沉沉，不宜久留。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "只要想起我们的翟家大小姐，就万事皆休，只想速走了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那叫管叔的还是甚么大司厨，只看他烧菜调味的手法来来去去都是那几招，便知弄出来的菜只是一般。若由我兄弟来弄他娘的几味，保证能吃得那些夫人小姐口水都流出来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_li",
      "speaker_name": "张厉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是告诉过你们吗？内府的奴仆不准到前府来，这么快就不守规矩了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhang_li",
      "text": "我们并不是要到前府，而是要到街上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_li",
      "speaker_name": "张厉",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "谁遣你们到外面去？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zhang_li",
      "text": "就是我自己。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_li",
      "speaker_name": "张厉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快回去，小姐吩咐，没有她的命令，你们两人不准离开府门半步。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zhang_li",
      "text": "这真是天大笑话，我们又不是囚犯，最多就是不干吧了。我们偏要离开。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_li",
      "speaker_name": "张厉",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好胆，是否不想活了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我这位兄弟就是脾气不好，三位大叔大人有大量，原谅则个。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "好汉不吃跟前亏，若惹出翟府的家将，我们这两个新扎高手就要立即完蛋大吉。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "刚才我曾学你般功聚双耳，立时听到大堂里传来轻细如无的均匀呼吸，此人比张厉那些九流角色厉害多了。显是府内真正的高手。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "老翟怕爱女给人再次掳走，当然会加派高手保护，现在我们难道回房睡觉吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "前门不通，便走后门，还要立即走。像张厉那种小人，不去向那女霸王搬弄是非才怪。所以买到东西后，须把家当藏在府内，以免给那恶婆娇缴了去自己练习母猴爬树。哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "可惜我们今晚就要溜，否则说不定不用去青楼，就可除掉这窝酿的青头身分。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人家是正经女儿家，若沾上了，可不能饱食远走，那时就烦死了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我倒没想过这点，想想还是去青楼干脆利落，唉，不过以后有素素姐在旁看着，很多事都要有所顾忌。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小兄弟，请到这里来说两句话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请坐。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本人屠叔方，乃龙头府内总管，专责府内安全，不知两位小兄弟要到哪裹去呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "只想溜到街外逛逛吧了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是人之常情。不过小姐吩咐，若两位兄弟不是有什么必须办的事，最好不要离开龙头府，一切待龙头老大回来再说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "那岂非当我们是囚犯吗。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们亦是迫不得已。请问两位和沈落雁究竟有何嫌隙！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "小姐有否告诉总管我们为何会到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小姐曾教图某莫要询问两位的事，只说须全力保护你们，图某当然要依命行事。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "总管跟大龙头有多少年了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位请放心直说，即管大龙头有甚么心事，亦不会瞒我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "最近发生在小姐身上的事，总管清楚吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然清楚，但不知两位指的是哪一此事。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "当然是有关她外游之事，小姐说过不准我们告诉任何人，总管有胆听吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们有胆说出来，我就有胆子听。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么说两位小兄弟当是身怀神功，否则怎能躲上屋梁，又能瞒过所有人的耳目。不过表面看来，两位虽体格轩昂，腰步沉稳，又气定神闲，但双目不现内芒，难道竟已达到反璞归真的境界吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "那是因为我们的内功别走蹊径，与一般武功大有分别，不信大可立即试试我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那我们就握握手好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "千万莫下重手！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个当然！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小兄弟的内劲果然非常怪异，似有如无，但又是深不可测。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 405,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "屠某信了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凭你们的身手，怎肯在膳房内受如此委屈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "有甚么法子，小姐的吩咐嘛。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但大龙头确是没有半点受了内伤的神态。这究竟是甚么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "小姐是否真给人掳走了，后来又给那祖君彦假惺惺作态的救回来。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "确有此事，但府内除屠某外，再没有人知道。此事非同小可，而目下我亦只能当作不知，一切要待大龙头回来再定夺。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "那我们可以出去逛逛吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更不能出去，现在沈落雁在府外布下人手，密切监视。这事我不敢报告小姐，怕她去闹事，所以只希望大龙头能早日归来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "大龙头到哪裹去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大龙头和密公正全力攻打兴洛仓，此战若胜，昏君将时日无多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "兴洛仓究竟是甚么仓，为何这么重要？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 449
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兴洛仓位于洛阳之东，荥阳之西的洛口，乃通济渠和黄河交交汇处。仓城周围二十馀里，设有三千个大窖，每窖储粮八千石，若得到这么一个仓城，我们瓦岗军十年内都不用忧心粮草不足了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "隋室这么布置不是很笨吗？岂非教人有明确的攻击目标？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "设仓时，哪想得到会有这么的一天。当年设仓，主要是用作积储租税米粮，以供朝廷使用。要知文帝建都长安，关中地区产粮常不足京城需求，从东方运去的漕运又有三门峡的险阻，费时费力，有了这些大粮仓后，京城就可保持粮食的稳定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "这么说，谁都不知大龙头会在何时回来了，我们岂非仍要每天砍柴挑水洗碗洗砾的捱下去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个容易，我会和小姐再作商量。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "text": "我们除了内功像点样子外，拳脚功夫却是一般，总管可否指点一下我们。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 479,
      "line_end": 481
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_shu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "屠叔方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "由于你们诚实谦虚，这回算得是找对人了。只念在你们远道仗义前来报讯，又曾救过素素，我就不会留私，让我传你们最自感得意的十二手擒拿截脉法，看看是否管用。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 40,
      "line_start": 483,
      "line_end": 487
    }
  ],
